44-7533.Appeals.

Any order or decision of the director made pursuant to the Property and Casualty Insurance Rate and Form Act may be appealed by any party in interest. The appeal shall be in accordance with the Administrative Procedure Act.

SourceLaws 2000, LB 1119, ยง 33.

Cross ReferencesAdministrative Procedure Act, see section 84-920.
